item.description:

By the way, we hit 70+ online yesterday before we had a little problem with some kids who were a little upset with how well extrania was doing.

[quote=“Xx Weed Xx, post:12, topic:440259”][quote author=Ix Soulcist xI link=topic=542933.msg3979435#msg3979435 date=1335060669]

I’ve been with Rene since his first server.

It seems this time around, Marc has been made the main owner.
[/quote]

What so Rene can sit back and take donations?[/quote]
I hold the donations.

[quote=“Bells, post:13, topic:440259”]Your channel buttons are incorrect for this gameframe, they should look like this if you want them to fit the gameframe.

Davidi2:

Please say you wont be selling staff positions anymore? :s

Of course not, there would probably be a lot of staff members if I did that
I would never sell staff positions on this server. The only other admin I will be having for a while is a server developer because I am really not the best developer so I need a lot of help with problems I run into and the server needs some more custom content.

Anyone who is looking to develop can contact me via PM. I only need one really good developer who can help add custom content.
